        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks JDH and Thiselton-Dyer for useful information.</p> 
<p>Is surprised <hi rend="italic">Mimosa albida</hi> is <hi rend="italic">not</hi> sensitive to water. Asks that they try again, or lend it to him.</p>  
<p>Remembers a walk in Brazil in great bed of <hi rend="italic">Mimosa</hi>.</p> 
            <p>After JDH left, CD was very bad, with much loss of memory and severe shocks continually passing through his brain.</p>
        </abstract>
